        "description": "<p><em>Jackie Chan Studio Fitness: J-MAT</em> is a fitness game that is controlled using a four button floor mat controller. The game features five different mini-games:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Step Lively</strong>: a mini-game where you must follow Jackie Chan's lead and step on the mat in time with him as orbs indicating where you should step fall from the top of the screen.</li>\n<li><strong>Vigorous Step</strong>: a rhythm game where you step on the mat in time to the music. You have a selection of ten songs to choose from.</li>\n<li><strong>Jackie's Action Run</strong>: a mini-game where you control Jackie Chan as he runs through the streets of Hong Kong. You must avoid obstacles be side-stepping, jumping, and squatting. During this mode you can encounter ninjas that you must to defeat by stepping on the area of the mat corresponding to each ninja.</li>\n<li><strong>Dash</strong>: a mini-game where you must step on the mad as fast as you can to see how many steps you can do in ten seconds.</li>\n<li><strong>Reflex</strong>: a mini-game where you must jump as quickly as you can when the game tells you in order to measure your average response time.</li>\n</ul>",
